  "description": {
    "zh": "现在让我们做点更现实的事情。有些东西不能走捷径，你得用经典的东西。这次只用栓动的怎么样？练一下，并用它击杀一些目标，不管是谁、在哪里、什么时候、在干什么。祝你好运，士兵。",
    "en": "Lets do something more specific now. You can't use the easy way for some things, you gotta use something classic. How about you get to use just a bolt-action rifle this time? And get some training with it, and eliminate a few targets, doesn't matter who, where or when. Good luck soldier."
